ğŸ” 4. Data Security

We apply industry-standard and modern security practices:

End-to-end encryption (E2EE) for all messages

TLS/HTTPS for all network traffic

Salted + hashed credentials

Zero-knowledge message architecture

Limited server access with strict authentication controls

Regular penetration tests & security audits

Even with these measures, no service is 100% immune to threats.
We encourage enabling device-level security features.

